建德站站房位于站场南侧，建筑面积12000平方米。站房外立面呈“人”字形，以红色为基调<ref name="electry">{{cite news|title=杭黄高铁最新照片！在建德站，高铁是行驶在“空中”的！|url=https://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_2405797|publisher=澎湃新闻|date=2018-09-03|accessdate=2018-10-09|archive-date=2019-05-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190520091225/https://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_2405797|dead-url=no}}</ref>。候车室内分别装饰有[[新安江水电站|新安江水电站]]以及[[新安江|新安江]]、[[兰江|兰江]]和[[富春江|富春江]]三江在古代[[严州府|严州府]]交汇为主题的浮雕<ref>{{cite news|title=记者实地探访杭黄铁路四座新建高铁站|url=http://hznews.hangzhou.com.cn/chengshi/content/2018-12/25/content_7121412_0.htm|publisher=杭州网|date=2018-12-25|accessdate=2019-01-15|archive-date=2019-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190116050013/http://hznews.hangzhou.com.cn/chengshi/content/2018-12/25/content_7121412_0.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
